rds%20ceremony%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20indeed%2C%20if%20you%20still%20don't%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20no%20need%20to%20be%20ashamed.%20The%20two%20actors%20were%20largely%20unknown%20before%20they%20were%20cast%20in%20the%20Canadian%20import%20%26quot%3BHeated%20Rivalry%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20romance%20drama%20that%20HBO%20head%20Casey%20Bloys%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2026%2F01%2F10%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia%2Fheated-rivalry-hbo-max-popularity.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Ba%20word-of-mouth%20sensation%26quot%3B%20after%20its%20first%20season%20debuted%20on%20the%20streamer%20in%20late%20November.%20The%20data%20bears%20this%20out%3A%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Luminate%2C%20viewership%20increased%20tenfold%20between%20the%20premiere%20and%20the%20finale%2C%20and%20the%20show%20has%20continued%20to%20accumulate%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20viewing%20minutes%20even%20after%20the%20season%20ended%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show%2C%20based%20on%20a%20book%20series%20by%20Rachel%20Reid%2C%20follows%20Ilya%20Rozanov%20(Storrie)%20and%20Shane%20Hollander%20(Williams)%2C%20two%20professional%20hockey%20players%20who%20embark%20upon%20a%20secret%20love%20affair.%20The%20series%20has%20quickly%20attracted%20a%20devoted%20following%20thanks%20to%20its%20steamy%20sex%20scenes%20and%20the%20onscreen%20chemistry%20between%20its%20co-leads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20personally%20vouch%20for%20the%20show's%20addictive%20appeal.%20Before%20I%20compulsively%20binged%20all%20six%20episodes%20in%20a%20single%20Saturday%20evening%2C%20declining%20a%20friend's%20invitation%20to%20go%20out%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20keep%20watching%2C%20I'd%20been%20asked%20about%20the%20show%20by%20no%20fewer%20than%20six%20people.%20These%20questions%20were%20usually%20phrased%20as%20assumptions%3A%20%26quot%3BYou've%20seen%20'Heated%20Rivalry%2C'%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20success%20story%20is