%20your%20head%20as%20you%20read%20that%20sentence.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20help%20but%20think%20of%20last%20year's%20announcement%20that%20Sam%20Mendes%20would%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-beatles-movies-sam-mendes-biopics-everything-we-know-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efour%20interconnected%20Beatles%20biopics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%20of%20trying%20to%20find%20promising%20newcomers%20who%20closely%20resembled%20and%20could%20embody%20the%20famous%20bandmates%2C%20the%20cast%20reveal%20reads%20like%20a%20standard%20response%20to%20the%20trivia%20question%2C%20%26quot%3BWhich%20young%20male%20actors%20have%20the%20most%20critical%20buzz%20and%20fanfare%20right%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20that%20Paul%20Mescal%20(%26quot%3BHamnet%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgladiator-2-review-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGladiator%20II%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B)%2C%20Harris%20Dickinson%20(%26quot%3BBabygirl%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-iron-claw-director-sean-durkin-interview-von-erich-family-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20Iron%20Claw%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B)%2C%20Joseph%20Quinn%20(%26quot%3BFantastic%20Four%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstranger-things-deaths-ranked-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStranger%20Things%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B)%2C%20and%20Barry%20Keoghan%20(%26quot%3BSaltburn%2C%26quot%3B%20Sabrina%20Carpenter's%20ex-boyfriend)%20don't%20have%20chops%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20that%20name%20recognition%20almost%20certainly%20came%20into%20play%20in%20casting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20obvious%20actor%20missing%20from%20that%20list%20would%20be%20Timoth%C3%A9e%20Chalamet%2C%20who%20helmed%20his%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimothee-chalamet-singing-a-complete-unknown-bob-