p%3ECourtesy%20of%20Reg%20Haid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Elias%20was%20delivered%2C%20Mary%20Ellen%20and%20I%20did%20two%20days%20of%20work%20with%20Svalinn%20trainers%2C%20where%20we%20learned%20how%20to%20handle%20him.%20I%20work%20with%20them%20daily%20to%20keep%20them%20up%20to%20date%20with%20their%20commands%2C%20and%20we%20return%20to%20the%20Svalinn%20ranch%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year%20to%20work%20with%20their%20trainers.%20It's%20an%20awesome%20couple%20of%20hours%20learning%20together.%20These%20dogs%20don't%20just%20require%20a%20financial%20investment%3B%20they%20also%20require%20an%20emotional%20and%20time%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270f93173-4bc9-434f-bc04-b3f5a20ee8ec%5C%22%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20explain%20how%20special%20these%20dogs%20are%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20equestrian%2C%20there's%20a%20feeling%20when%20you're%20riding%20a%20really%20intelligent%20horse%20that's%20transcendent.%20That's%20the%20closest%20I%20can%20come%20to%20describing%20the%20value%20of%20Svalinn%20dogs.%20Quite%20frankly%2C%20there's%20an%20emotional%20connection%20that%20I%20didn't%20anticipate.%20I%20never%20knew%20I%20could%20love%20a%20dog%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20had%20read%20this%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20would%20have%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20guy's%20crazy.%26quot%3B%20I%20know%20how%20it%20sounds%2C%20but%20Elias%20and%20Rooster%20are%20just%20different.%20They%20have%20all%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20having%20a%20dog%20with%20none%20of%20the%20inconvenience%3A%20no%20barking%20or%20misbehavior.%20The%20intellect%20and%20emotional%20intelligence%20they%20have%20are%20worth%20every%20penny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-two-svalinn-dogs-transformed-my-life-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768245841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F