3EHrushikesh%20planted%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20between%20mango%20and%20%3Cem%3Eamla%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20gooseberry)%20trees.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20there%20was%20no%20harm%20in%20growing%20aloe%20vera%20on%20my%20farm%2C%20even%20if%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20generate%20immediate%20income.%20I%20knew%20that%20aloe%20vera%20could%20work%20wonders%20as%20a%20termite%20repellent%20and%20would%20help%20protect%20my%20mango%20trees%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20graduate%2C%20who%20holds%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20horticulture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20offline%20exhibitions%20organised%20in%20Satara%2C%20he%20often%20came%20across%20small%20entrepreneurs%20selling%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F237401%2Fman-earns-lakhs-aloe-vera-organic-online-fresh-products-self-help-groups-inspiring-rural-development-meghalaya-rongram-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealoe%20vera%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CInspired%20by%20the%20idea%2C%20I%20started%20preparing%20products%20like%20soaps%2C%20shampoos%2C%20and%20aloe%20vera%20juice.%20But%20this%20did%20not%20bring%20me%20good%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20his%20expertise%20in%20horticulture%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20utilise%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreader%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoter.%20%E2%80%9CInsect%20thrips%20damage%20the%20buds%20and%20leaves%20of%20crops.%20I%20once%20mixed%20aloe%20vera%20with%20fish%20oil%20and%20sprayed%20it%20on%20crops.%20Pests%20and%20animals%20dislike%20it%20because%20of%20its%20bitter%20taste.%20I%20found%20this%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20pest%20repellent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2